  }, "SanDisk 32GB Ultra Fit USB 3.1 Flash Drive"), " by using my morning run to literally run and pick one up from a Curry\u2019s a couple kilometres away as I wanted to get the build done and start copying files in the same weekend \uD83D\uDE05"), mdx("p", null, "You can also buy USB sticks that have a proper SSD inside (", mdx("a", {
